  "2026-07-14T00:09:50.089Z",codex-gpt5,"Implementation evidence: Sentry capture now suppresses only typed CommandError instances with numeric exit codes representing handled command outcomes; raw/untyped failures remain captured. Dedicated regressions and all exact-tree strict gates pass at 100/100/100/100 coverage."
